our chance to say

31
00:02:12,549 --> 00:02:15,510
what improvements we want
to see in the office

32
00:02:15,593 --> 00:02:17,887
and also in our policies.

33
00:02:17,971 --> 00:02:18,972
Right, guys?

34
00:02:20,014 --> 00:02:21,015
Mm-hmm.

35
00:02:22,100 --> 00:02:25,395
That's great. I'm all about
bringing in improvements.

36
00:02:25,478 --> 00:02:28,106
And of course, I want
our office to run perfectly.

37
00:02:29,691 --> 00:02:31,317
Like me.

38
