since she's our manager.

58
00:03:59,322 --> 00:04:00,323
Yeah.

59
00:04:00,990 --> 00:04:02,408
How about our team leader?

60
00:04:02,492 --> 00:04:04,535
I think it'll be more fair
if we just draw lots.

61
00:04:04,619 --> 00:04:05,662
No, no, no.

62
00:04:05,745 --> 00:04:06,704
Instead of drawing lots,

63
00:04:06,788 --> 00:04:08,373
let's do it
the old-fashioned way.

64
00:04:09,666 --> 00:04:13,461
Well, they seem
intimidated by you.

65
00:04:13,544 --> 00:04:16,714
Maybe that's why
no one wanted to speak up.

66
00:04:16,798 --> 00:04:19,676
Sec. Kim, I know
they are your friends,

67
00:04:19,759 --> 00:04:22,929
but they are also the future
leaders of the company.

68
00:04:23,012 --> 00:04:24,889
So, they should learn
to speak up,

69
00:04:24,973 --> 00:04:26,307
even in my presence,

70
00:04:26,391 --> 00:04:28,601
no matter how intimidating
I may seem.

71
00:04:30,395 --> 00:04:34,232
