94
00:05:38,296 --> 00:05:39,297
Shh.

95
00:05:43,301 --> 00:05:44,802
Well, you see,

96
00:05:44,886 --> 00:05:48,347
I saw Cyrus's sobriety coin.

97
00:05:48,431 --> 00:05:50,725
Don't you know that it's bad
for recovering alcoholics

98
00:05:50,808 --> 00:05:52,852
